Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:34.07,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an7\pos(1530,730)}风的回应

Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被这里的酒香吸引而来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 莫非你也是那家伙的鹡鸰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 这个人真的和我没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不准你们对她出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰翅 稍稍给他尝些苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记拜托他给我录制高画质了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐 快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到 到底在哪儿呢 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 你事情忙完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没闲心管说这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人被惩罚部队掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子…碎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(注：前者「さらわれた」与后者「皿割れた」发音相同)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝都码头5号仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松 松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.104(No.104)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人在一起 这下变得很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人在码头的仓库 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 绝对错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就闯入的话 会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也制定下作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在哪还有制定计划的空闲 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少带上手机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次逃脱作战时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惩罚部队进行了激烈的苦战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个的话 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒臭味…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说你在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒 不行了 眼睛也昏昏…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们快跑了都
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把他们抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们啊 小看我们… 惩罚部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚部队 惩罚部队呐… 总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 差不多是时候来真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 小结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 比起买东西大战的时候 快了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 皆人 我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别装淡定噢 大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你这么认为？ 露点酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧 你肯定看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是看到了 还是能看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夏朗意外的男人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦 这状况有点不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是2对1 你觉得你有胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰翅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让你们逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苇牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接把No.88叫来不就不用受这罪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与鹡鸰和苇牙都无关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不要任何人为了我而受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那样的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心好痛 这便是这个男孩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此纯粹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不问你想不想要我 现在我想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们担心 为我们哭泣 爱着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要的这样的苇牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管你那儿吹来的风不是那么的可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间还说 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老是睡不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得今天挺安静的 大家去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风飘动吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 你成为最后一个了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是指…就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该去做晚饭的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好热 我的身体中热浪四处乱撞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那个人的思念也温暖的融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 终于能从之前的恋情中解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽化…了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我缔结誓约的风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请为苇牙吹散乌云
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前 好像有过这经历
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰No.03 风花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认可你做我的苇牙 新欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(注 「恋」的发音与鲤鱼的「鲤」相同){\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后多多关照咯 我的苇牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐 你也羽化了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 小结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第五羽鹡鸰了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 给我说的失恋的事情是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢是不需要理由的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我说过的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这种口气跟我说话的只有No.01和Game Master而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样 大家要好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苇牙君 皆人 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强算是给我看了点有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那个孩子没能及时赶到真的很遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是无法接通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是遇到什么事情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨蛋哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是哥哥有急事 来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为何是老妈来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我不会对她做坏事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这话带给美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为样体的No.88被工作员抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把她夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知恋鸟 似乎是鹡鸰的别称
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓 人会在爱与被爱中 成长得更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能在将来振翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让世界充满爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对于忘记完成这项使命的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少来保护雏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是 缘系鹡鸰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 教雏鸟们学会爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 没事吧 有没有什么疼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 这里是医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBI直营的帝都医院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告诉我 在这儿 苇牙大人都能够得到免费的治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告诉你 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑部似乎没有异常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时性意识障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天就可以出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎瘦了点呢 有好好吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我约好去和由佳里见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经联络过她 说你有急事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小结那儿听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何 怎么老妈你会在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 高美是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识我老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该从何说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾告诉过你说 我在制药公司工作是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBI 鹡鸰计划主任 佐桥高美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于各种情况 暂时由我来负责佐桥皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBI？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高美女士给我做过很多调整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调…调整？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我去换下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 小结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 我有点事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就想看看小结你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我在这儿 您知道得很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到母公司 就能获得很多的情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 高美女士也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没能和红翼战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍迟了那么些 没能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你教唆他们的吧 鸦羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小结确实发生过机能停止是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 虽然小结似乎不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰纹也消失过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 身体发出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.08 缘系鹡鸰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让结女我来做你们的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.08？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机能停止后的再启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部浮现的08的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 发生的都是让人完全搞不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.08到底是何人 高美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候把这事说出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该称呼我母亲大人 不是吗 月海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 这种时候 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是月海我一生的过失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母…母…母上大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那事 不清楚的地方也很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结本身应该有自己的理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结自己的理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEVEL 4的鹡鸰被… 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去工作了 拜拜了 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEVEL 4？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指机能停止的伤害等级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有5个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LEVEL 4 是相当严重的伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦羽大人你身上有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结呢 你必须变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比她还要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 实现我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为最后的两羽鹡鸰 在世界中翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再高兴的互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 小草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是佐桥你的归来庆祝会噢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 没发生什么大事 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草 我可是超超超担心的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起呢 小草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 此次是我不注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错误而让苇牙受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 回来了啊 真是灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钿女 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你鹡鸰数量又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了 这个 钿女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 真的很厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 没看到风花小姐的身影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 风花小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这副装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 对新婚妻子还使用小姐二字 叫我风花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出云庄 禁止穿着裸露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉 你表情好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.19被黑色的鹡鸰…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 之后是风花No.03
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不想惹恼北方的般若吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把北方的狩猎交给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相应的 拜托了 千惠的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钿女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉说这种衣服不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我看看钿女你的衣柜收藏行不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话请便噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿哪一件 皆人会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在这儿夺取她的鹡鸰纹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 你成为最后一个了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为任何人的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不打算成为
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有了第五羽鹡鸰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人难不成你想搞后宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你不就是后宫主管咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你练上茶的方法都没搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说现在的年轻人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想的这些事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有完没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四羽 最后的一羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也请多多关照

