Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.68,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}ココロを強く繋ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:13.68,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}将心紧紧系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.56,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}変わる世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.56,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}瞬息万变的世上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.84,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}鐘が響くゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.84,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}钟声回响耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:24.07,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}終わりなきタタカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:24.07,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}没有终结的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:27.70,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}すべてを引き裂いても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:27.70,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}即使一切都已碎裂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.81,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}君の微笑みただ信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.81,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我依旧只相信你的微笑
